race.comment: OUR BOY CHOPPER (8) jumps from box 8 for the first time after placing latest at Capalaba (20.04) in a Free For All. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Key chance in this line up. BYE BYE SWIPER (2) drew the inside and won last time at this track and distance (18.95) after spotting a start, scoring by one length. Leading player again. MANDANDA (4) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2.25 lengths at Capalaba in a handy 19.97 beating Bundy Trigger. Form from his last run is proving strong. Sure to measure up. PORT FOR SHORE (7) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.
